<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Expense Splitter - Objectives & Problem Statement</title>
    <style>
        /* --- Color Palette & Fonts --- */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-brown: #896a55; 
            --dark-charcoal: #322f2c; 
            --light-beige: #f6f3ed; 
            --text-dark: #222222;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--light-beige);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Animations --- */
        @keyframes fadeSlideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .animate-item {
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeSlideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Delays for cascading effect */
        .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

        /* --- Page Header --- */
        .page-header {
            background-color: var(--primary-brown);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* --- Problem Statement Section --- */
        .problem-section {
            background-color: var(--dark-charcoal);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 80px 10%;
        }

        .section-title-light {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary-brown);
        }

        .problem-intro {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .problem-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .problem-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-brown);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .problem-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .problem-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--light-beige);
        }

        .problem-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* --- Objectives Section --- */
        .objectives-section {
            padding: 80px 10%;
            background-color: var(--light-beige);
        }

        .section-title-dark {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--dark-charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title-dark::after {
            content: '';
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--primary-brown);
            display: block;
            margin: 15px auto 0;
        }

        .objectives-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .objective-item {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .objective-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .objective-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: rgba(137, 106, 85, 0.15); /* Faint brown */
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .objective-item h4 {
            color: var(--dark-charcoal);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .objective-item p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="page-header animate-item">
        <h1>Motivation & Objectives</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Problem Statement Section -->
    <section class="problem-section">
        <h2 class="section-title-light animate-item delay-1">The Problem Statement</h2>
        <p class="problem-intro animate-item delay-1">Shared expenses naturally degrade into financial confusion and interpersonal friction.[cite: 1]</p>
        
        <div class="problem-grid">
            <div class="problem-card animate-item delay-2">
                <h3>01. High Manual Effort</h3>
                <p>Groups rely on spreadsheets, WhatsApp messages, or memory — all highly time-consuming and error-prone methods for tracking shared costs.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-item delay-2">
                <h3>02. Frequent Calculation Errors</h3>
                <p>Manual arithmetic inevitably leads to mistakes in splitting bills, causing under or over-payment and repeated disputes among members.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-item delay-3">
                <h3>03. No Transparency</h3>
                <p>Existing informal methods lack the full Financial history. Members cannot easily verify who paid what and who owes whom.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-item delay-3">
                <h3>04. Lack of Settlement Tracking</h3>
                <p>There is no mechanism to mark debts as settled, leading to old, unpaid amounts lingering indefinitely without resolution.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-item delay-4">
                <h3>05. Privacy & Security Gaps</h3>
                <p>Sharing financial data through messaging apps exposes sensitive information with no encryption or access control.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Objectives Section -->
    <section class="objectives-section">
        <h2 class="section-title-dark animate-item">Project Objectives</h2>
        
        <div class="objectives-grid">
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-1">
                <div class="objective-number">01</div>
                <h4>Web Application</h4>
                <p>Web application engineered to manage shared expenses efficiently.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-1">
                <div class="objective-number">02</div>
                <h4>Authentication</h4>
                <p>Allow users to securely register and log in using email/password with encrypted credential management.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-2">
                <div class="objective-number">03</div>
                <h4>Group Management</h4>
                <p>Enable users to create expense groups, add members, and record shared expense events with descriptions.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-2">
                <div class="objective-number">04</div>
                <h4>Algorithmic Calculation</h4>
                <p>Automatically compute exact individual balances — who owes whom and how much — with zero manual arithmetic.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-3">
                <div class="objective-number">05</div>
                <h4>Debt Settlement</h4>
                <p>Allow users to mark payments as settled and maintain a clear record of all transactions.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-3">
                <div class="objective-number">06</div>
                <h4>History Tracking</h4>
                <p>Maintain a complete history of all group expenses and settlements for full financial transparency.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-4">
                <div class="objective-number">07</div>
                <h4>Intuitive Interface</h4>
                <p>Provide a highly user-friendly interface prioritising clear data entry, readable balances, and minimal friction.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="objective-item animate-item delay-4">
                <div class="objective-number">08</div>
                <h4>Secure Architecture</h4>
                <p>Build a secure web app using encryption to protect user transaction data.[cite: 1]</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
